node.text: If you're in the thick of postpartum and spending your days trying to figure out just who this little person is and what all their many cries might mean and if/how/when you'll ever sleep again, let this 👆🏽 bring you hope. In what will one day seem like the blink of an eye, you'll be sharing inside jokes and too-wet kisses, and they'll know you're their person and you'll know they're the best thing that ever happened to you, and you'll fit together in your favorite spot just the way you always have, but with a little more certainty, a little more confidence, and maybe, just maybe, a little more rest. 💕@lily_jieru
